name: Half Day Visit
description: A half day visit lasts up to 7 hours and includes supervised playtime with other dogs and outdoor walks.

name: Full Day Visit
description: Your four-legger can play the day away with other dogs.  Full day visits last 7 to 12 hours and include multiple outdoor walks and a healthy snack.

name: Overnight Stay
description: Book an overnight stay for your special four-legger! Includes dinner, an evening walk, and a tasty goodnight treat!

name: Swimming Lessons
description: This one-on-one swimming opportunity gives your special four-legger the chance to work with one of our trainers in our on-site doggie pool.  A 2-hour sessions includes a walk break and healthy snack.
